                        <br><br>
                        <p class="lead">This guide provides the best practices you need to optimize the following Dynamics 365 (D365) functions:</p>
                        <ul class="defaultBody">
                            <li>Solutions</li>
                            <li>Fields</li>   
                            <li>Relationships</li>
                            <li>Forms</li>
                            <li>Views</li>   
                            <li>Model-driven Apps</li>  
                            <li>Processes</li>
                            <li>Web Resources</li>   
                            <li>Plug-ins</li>  
                        </ul>
                    </div>
